com.gridgraph.storage

Class HeapGraphStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gridgraph.storage.HeapGraphStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IGraphStorage, IMessageStorage

    public class HeapGraphStorage
extends Object
implements IGraphStorage
    A HeapGraphStorage is a concrete IGraphStorage to provide graph database storage for single graph.
